{"tid":367244,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底點先可以遷就另一半同時保持自我","createTime":"2017-08-20T15:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T17:26:17.000Z","uid":68284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e661ce07ab1c2b3f2d701285618461d43ef0afe","tid":367244,"uid":68284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"如題，成日見人講好多時太遷就另一半會令人失去自我，其實何謂失去自我。<br />\n兩個人相處唔想咁多磨擦，多啲遷就對方我覺得好正常，但喱啲唔係就係磨合咩，點先係失去自我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心問"},{"pid":"965a9f813ed3ba2926e738794f58a2f2b6c155d0","tid":367244,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"當你嘅價值觀覺得一個行為係錯嘅，但就以愛催眠自己改變睇法（？）"},{"pid":"ba30142cd4418cf8bd19775b9d12c7690cbd1134","tid":367244,"uid":43518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"俾對方知道自己底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如對方成日遲到，你底線係等一個鐘就算<br />\n但對方知你一定會等佢，慢慢變本加厲，你就等等下等成3個鐘"},{"pid":"271dd0ee0534be3e871ed8a58c60762033913b4d","tid":367244,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:39:46.000Z","msg":"當你明白一樣野：not worth"},{"pid":"c9edbfae00c421fcd4297045648422efe23fffff","tid":367244,"uid":102179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"搵一個唔須要遷就都配合到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ff265c26344d3a79cdf221644c4c9b8704f2cb","tid":367244,"uid":68284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你嘅價值觀覺得一個行為係錯嘅，但就以愛催眠自己改變睇法（？）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，又好似真係會咁"}]}